OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FSir Keir said at Prime Minister's
OL,8,Fquestions last week that he wants to
OL,9,Frestore the payments to more
OL,10,Fpensioners, following pressure from
OL,11,Fcampaigners, signalling a partial U-
OL,12,Fturn on one of Labour's first
OL,13,Fannouncements in Government.
OL,15,FHe claimed that the UK's improving
OL,16,Feconomic prospects could allow for the
OL,17,Fmove at the next fiscal event. The
OL,18,Fpartial U-turn came as ministers are
OL,19,Fcontinuing to face calls to scrap the
OL,20,Ftwo-child benefit cap.
