OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FSpeaking to Sky News on Thursday
OL,8,Fevening, Chief Secretary to the
OL,9,FTreasury Mr Jones was asked about
OL,10,FReform UK's commitments on both the
OL,11,Fwinter fuel and benefit cap policies.
OL,13,F"All of those things cost money," Mr
OL,14,FJones said.
OL,16,F"It's right that we set out the detail
OL,17,Fand how we're going to pay for those
OL,18,Fin a proper and orderly way."
