OL,7,FHe added: "We're sticking to the
OL,8,Fprinciple that millionaires shouldn't
OL,9,Fbe getting subsidy for their energy
OL,10,Fbills from the government, so winter
OL,11,Ffuel payments will still be targeted
OL,12,Fto those that need it the most."
OL,14,FMr Jones also touched on the
OL,15,FGovernment's approach to child
OL,16,Fpoverty, telling the same programme
OL,17,Fthat "we're a Labour government we
OL,18,Fwant child poverty to be falling in
OL,19,Fthis country, not rising".
